      <textAnnotation id="sid-9E7C185F-49A6-45C4-AA1C-0D0BA32BD95C" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-FA6E5766-8ABB-44FF-AC00-F7ADEE1ABED4" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Subledgers: AP &amp; AR from CFIN, Assets &amp; Others from IP &amp; IF</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4845AF68-F5E7-4F97-A6D1-432009766292" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>i.Cfin ACDOCA vs ECC
ii.Cfin ACDOCA vs IF
iii.Cfin ACDOCA vs IP</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-CF8ABB58-35A4-4732-8904-5E92A1BE5FB9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Mass download of JEs would be done for backup purpose (covered by transaction processing)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2F73BA4A-FA80-49FD-91A2-6BB48B3C2D0B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Middleware Connection between SAP and Blackline is set (Through FPRI0600_CFIN, FPRI0600_IP, FPRI0600_IF)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B6F10EC3-B58F-4727-ADE5-4F29B58BAF2C" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-172F9A63-EF22-4401-9EBD-A8A2593DC2F9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Asset List - FPRXV041
FAA Impairment system Subledger - FPRE0572
FAA 167400 System Subledger - TBD</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-60ADF12E-D86A-400E-B00F-24FDF5A8FBD0" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>ATB Report - FPRXR010
Net Revenue Walk - Remain in Plutus
Vistex Rebate Balance - Remain in Plutus</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-06816D0F-60D0-4A44-8C8F-5825C822FC33" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>FIS Treasury and Risk Manager (Quantum)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-48D0C7C4-1F11-44E8-B64E-6DB2B3AD6846" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Citidirect and other bank statement report - Remain in Citidirect</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A32AE1B3-194A-4ED2-97BA-9BB8163FA35C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Harbor Flex Report - Remain in Harbor</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-355745C1-44BC-4F87-9472-B2A92D1E4D5C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Concur - Remain in Concur
Headcount Report - Remain as is
PRR &amp; JV from vendor - Remain as is</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A7CEA137-BFBC-4231-BD33-0BD656B92B54" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>FPRXV025</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-65C4230F-765D-4B9F-A24D-AAC3832A7E6D" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-70B75B44-41EA-4367-9CE0-7E62D6DBB4E2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>ONESOURCE Standard Reports to be used for the same</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower:FPR_Finance Plan To Report
Process Group: DC_Manage Accounting and Control Data
Process: DC-030-060B Perform Reconciliations_R3</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0D49A23C-6157-4A8F-B58C-11C0CDAD157B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>&gt; Auto-certify Subledgers

&gt; Perform Reconciliation in Blackline
i.Ensure there is no line items of open items more then the late JE's threshold
ii.GL &amp; Subledgers source of records from Cfin to Blackine (manual reconcilation- journal entries downloaded from Fiori App) 

&gt; Cash Reconciliation
 </text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
